headline: Uber Expands AI Data Platform to Power Next-Gen Enterprise and AI Lab Needs
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, June 20, 2025--Uber Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: UBER) today announced a major expansion of its AI data services business, Uber AI Solutions, making its technology platform available to support AI labs and enterprises around the world. The new offerings include customized data solutions for building smarter AI models and agents, global digital task networks, and tools to help companies build and test AI models more efficiently.
